ple.com/users</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-sm mt-xs text-sm text-content-secondary"><span>200</span><span>JSON</span></div></div><div class="flex gap-xs shrink-0"><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md font-medium transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:ring-offset-2 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed text-content-secondary hover:text-content-primary hover:bg-surface-secondary px-sm py-xs text-sm  ">Edit</button><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md font-medium transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:ring-offset-2 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed text-content-secondary hover:text-content-primary hover:bg-surface-secondary px-sm py-xs text-sm  ">Del</button></div></div></div><div class="bg-surface-card border border-border rounded-md p-md transition-opacity "><div class="flex items-start gap-sm"><label class="inline-flex items-center gap-sm cursor-pointer"><button role="switch" aria-checked="true" class="relative inline-flex h-5 w-9 shrink-0 rounded-full border-2 border-transparent transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:ring-offset-2 bg-primary"><span class="pointer-events-none inline-block h-4 w-4 rounded-full bg-white shadow transform transition-transform translate-x-4"></span></button></label><div class="flex-1 min-w-0"><div class="flex items-center gap-xs flex-wrap"><span class="inline-flex items-center px-sm py-xs text-xs font-semibold rounded bg-surface-secondary text-content-secondary " style="background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.125); color: rgb(59, 130, 246);">POST</span><span class="font-mono text-base text-content-primary truncate">https://api.example.com/posts</span></div><div class="flex items-center gap-sm mt-xs text-sm text-content-secondary"><span>201</span><span>JSON</span></div></div><div class="flex gap-xs shrink-0"><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md font-medium transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:ring-offset-2 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed text-content-secondary hover:text-content-primary hover:bg-surface-secondary px-sm py-xs text-sm  ">Edit</button><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md font-medium transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:ring-offset-2 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed text-content-secondary hover:text-content-primary hover:bg-surface-secondary px-sm py-xs text-sm  ">Del</button></div></div></div></div></div>"`;
